The paper discusses a framework for formal specification and analysis of interactive systems, with a focus on spatio-temporal aspects. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including software engineering (cs.SE), programming languages (cs.PL), logic in computer science (cs.LO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, given the emphasis on specification and analysis, cs.SE is the most likely category, followed by cs.PL and cs.LO. The other categories are less likely but still possible, depending on the specific focus of the paper.
